The background templates are formed as subsets of all probe electron candidates used in the denominator of the identification efficiency calculation. The probes for the background template are required to be reconstructed as electrons with a matching track that satisfies track quality criteria; however, they are required to fail some of the identification requirements, namely the requirements on wstot\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
