As described in Sect. 3, for the 2012 data, a new track reconstruction algorithm has been introduced in order to improve the reconstruction of electrons that have undergone significant bremsstrahlung. Figure 20 also compares the reconstruction efficiencies measured in the 2011 and 2012 data. The new track fitting algorithm improves the overall electron reconstruction efficiency by ∼\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
